quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  18,60,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo sagataa makko on: \"Mi seerataa haa mi yottoo ka fottirde maaje ɗen ɗiɗi, maaɗun mi wuloo jamaanu"
  18,61,"Tuma nde ɓe yottoyinoo hakkonde majje ɓe yejjiti linngil maɓɓe ngil, ngil jogitii laawol maggil ka maayo wuddere"
  18,62,"Nde ɓe lummbunoo o [Muusaa] maakani sagataa makko on: \"Anndanii en sojjaari=bottaari men ndin, gomɗii en hawrii e nduu yaadu men ɗoo tampere"
  18,63,"O wi'i: \"A yi'ii, nde sorunoɗen ka fetere, min mi yejjuno linngil ngil, yejjintinaali lan fii maggil si wanaa Seytaane nde mi anndita ngil, ngil jogitii laawol maggil ka maayo no hawnori"
  18,64,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Ko ɗon ko wonɗen ɗaɓɓude kon [woni], ɓe ruttii e ɓatteeji maɓɓe fillitagol"
  18,65,"Ɓe tawoyi jeyaaɗo immorde e jeyaaɓe Amen Men Okki mo Hinnayee immorde ka Amen, Men Anndini mo immorde e Amen Ganndal"
  18,66,"Muusaa maakani mo: \"Enee [a accay] mi jokkete fii yo a anndinan goɗɗun e ko anndinaɗaa kon Peewal"
  18,67,"[Khadiru] maaki: \"Pellet, an a hattantaake muñal wonndugol e an"
  18,68,Ko honno munñuretaa e dow kon ko a huɓindoraa ɗun ganndal
  18,69,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"A taway lan si Alla Muuyi ko mi munñiiɗo, mi yeddataa yamiroore maa"
  18,70,"O maaki: \"Si a jokkay lam wata a lanndo lan gaayi huunde haa mi yeewte immorde e mayre janta"